    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Institutul Internațional de Cercetare și Formare pentru Promovarea Femeilor"@ro, "Mednarodni raziskovalni in izobraževalni inštitut Združenih narodov za napredek žensk"@sl, "Mezinárodní výzkumný a vzdělávací institut pro problematiku postavení žen"@cs, "Международен учебен и научноизследователски институт за напредъка на жените"@bg, "Tarptautinis tyrimų ir mokymo institutas moterims skatinti"@lt, "Internationales Forschungs- und Ausbildungsinstitut zur Förderung der Frau"@de, "Међурегионални институт УН за истраживање о криминалу и правосуђу"@sr, "Institiúid Idirnáisiúnta Taighde agus Oiliúna do Chur ar Aghaidh na mBan"@ga, "Istituto internazionale delle Nazioni Unite per la ricerca e la formazione del progresso delle donne"@it, "International Research and Training Institute for the Advancement of Women"@en, "Międzynarodowy Instytut Kształcenia i Badań nad Awansem Kobiet"@pl, "Det Internationale Forsknings- og Uddannelsesinstitut for Kvinder"@da, "FN:s internationella forsknings- och utvecklingsinstitut för kvinnors utveckling"@sv, "Starptautiskais Pētniecības un mācību institūts sieviešu izaugsmei"@lv, "Instituto Internacional de Investigaciones y Capacitación para la Promoción de la Mujer"@es, "Međunarodni istraživački i izobrazbeni institut Ujedinjenih naroda za unaprjeđenje položaja žena"@hr, "Internationaal Onderzoeks- en Opleidingsinstituut voor de vooruitgang van de vrouw"@nl, "Nemzetközi Kutató és Oktató Intézet a Nők Előrehaladásáért"@hu, "Διεθνές Ινστιτούτο έρευνας και εκπαίδευσης των Ηνωμένων Εθνών για την προώθηση των γυναικών"@el, "Institut international de recherche et de formation pour la promotion de la femme"@fr, "Rahvusvaheline teadus- ja koolitusinstituut naiste arengu edendamiseks"@et, "Medzinárodný výskumný a vzdelávací inštitút pre zlepšenie postavenia žien"@sk, "Istitut Internazzjonali ta’ Riċerka u Taħriġ għall-Avvanz tan-Nisa"@mt, "Kansainvälinen tutkimus- ja koulutusinstituutti naisten aseman parantamiseksi"@fi, "Instituto Internacional de Investigação e de Formação para a Promoção da Mulher"@pt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "UN-INSTRAW was the leading UN institute devoted to research, training and knowledge management to achieve gender equality and women’s empowerment. Through alliance building with governments around the world, the UN System, academia, civil society, the private sector and other actors, UN-INSTRAW conducted action-oriented research, created synergies for knowledge management, and built capacity in organizations working toward gender equality. UN-INSTRAW worked to promote women’s security, development and participation through three programs: Human Security, Development and Human Rights."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "UN_INSTRAW"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001247"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "UN_INSTRAW"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "INSTRAW"@sk, "INSTRAW"@fr, "INSTRAW"@el, "INSTRAW"@es, "INSTRAW"@pl, "INSTRAW"@da, "INSTRAW"@de, "INSTRAW"@fi, "INSTRAW"@cs, "INSTRAW"@it, "INSTRAW"@nl, "INSTRAW"@lt, "INSTRAW"@ga, "INSTRAW"@sl, "INSTRAW"@hr, "INSTRAW"@et, "ÜRO Naiste Olukorra Parandamise Rahvusvaheline Uurimis- ja Koolitusinstituut"@et, "INSTRAW"@sv, "INSTRAW"@hu, "INSTRAW"@ro, "INSTRAW"@lv, "МУНИНЖ"@bg, "INSTRAW"@mt, "INSTRAW"@pt, "INSTRAW"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UN_INSTRAW_1976_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "UN_INSTRAW";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "UN_INSTRAW";
