    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "De Forenede Nationers Institut for Nedrustningsforskning"@da, "Istituto delle Nazioni Unite per la ricerca sul disarmo"@it, "Ινστιτούτο των Ηνωμένων Εθνών για την Έρευνα περί του Αφοπλισμού"@el, "Institiúid na Náisiún Aontaithe um Thaighde ar an Dí-armáil"@ga, "Istitut tan-Nazzjonijiet Uniti għar-riċerka dwar id-diżarm"@mt, "Instituto das Nações Unidas para a Investigação sobre o Desarmamento"@pt, "VN-Instituut voor Ontwapeningsonderzoek"@nl, "Az Egyesült Nemzetek Leszerelési Kutatóintézete"@hu, "Institut der Vereinten Nationen für Abrüstungsforschung"@de, "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas Atbruņošanās pētniecības institūts"@lv, "Jungtinių Tautų nusiginklavimo tyrimo institutas"@lt, "Instituto de las Naciones Unidas de Investigación sobre el Desarme"@es, "Institut Ujedinjenih naroda za studije o razoružanju"@hr, "United Nations Institute for Disarmament Research"@en, "Institut des Nations unies pour la recherche sur le désarmement"@fr, "ÜRO Desarmeerimisuuringute Instituut"@et, "Институт УН за истраживање разоружања"@sr, "YK:n aseidenriisunnan tutkimuslaitos"@fi;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The United Nations Institute for Disarmament Research is a voluntarily funded autonomous institute within the United Nations. An impartial actor, the Institute generates ideas and promotes action on disarmament and security. Based in Geneva, UNIDIR is centrally positioned to assist the international community in developing the practical, innovative thinking needed to find solutions to the challenges of today and tomorrow. UNIDIR brings together states, international organizations, civil society, the private sector and academia so that we may work together – internationally, regionally and locally – to build and implement creative solutions that will benefit all states and peoples."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COB0001241"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "UNIDIR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "UNIDIR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Institutul Națiunilor Unite pentru Cercetare în Domeniul Dezarmării"@ro, "Inštitút OSN pre výskum odzbrojenia"@sk, "FN:s institut för nedrustningsforskning"@sv, "Inštitut ZN za preučevanje razorožitve"@sl, "ANO Atbruņošanās pētniecības institūts"@lv, "Instytut ONZ ds. Badań nad Rozbrojeniem"@pl, "Výzkumný institut OSN pro otázky odzbrojení"@cs, "UNIDIR"@hr, "UNIDIR"@da, "UNIDIR"@pt, "UNIDIR"@cs, "UNIDIR"@nl, "UNIDIR"@sk, "UNIDIR"@de, "UNIDIR"@mt, "ЮНИДИР"@bg, "UNIDIR"@fi, "UNIDIR"@pl, "UNIDIR"@ga, "UNIDIR"@en, "UNIDIR"@it, "UNIDIR"@lv, "UNIDIR"@fr, "UNIDIR"@ro, "UNIDIR"@el, "UNIDIR"@et, "UNIDIR"@hu, "UNIDIR"@lt, "FN’s Institut for Nedrustningsforskning"@da, "UNIDIR"@sl, "UNIDIR"@es, "Институт на ООН по разоръжаването"@bg, "YK:n aseidenriisuntatutkimusinstituutti"@fi, "Unidir"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNIDIR_1980_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "UNIDIR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "UNIDIR";
