    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Centro delle Nazioni Unite per lo sviluppo regionale"@it, "Център за регионално развитие на Обединените нации"@bg, "Centro de las Naciones Unidas para el Desarrollo Regional"@es, "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas Reģionālās attīstības centrs"@lv, "Ċentru tan-Nazzjonijiet Uniti għall-Iżvilupp Reġjonali"@mt, "De Forenede Nationers Center for Regionaludvikling"@da, "Centre des Nations unies pour le développement régional"@fr, "YK:n alueellisen kehityksen keskus"@fi, "Zentrum der Vereinten Nationen für Regionalentwicklung"@de, "Egyesült Nemzetek Regionális Fejlesztési Központja"@hu, "Centro das Nações Unidas para o Desenvolvimento Regional"@pt, "Lárionad na Náisiún Aontaithe um Fhorbairt Réigiúnach"@ga, "Centar Ujedinjenih naroda za regionalni razvoj"@hr, "Κέντρο Περιφερειακής Ανάπτυξης των Ηνωμένων Εθνών"@el, "Jungtinių Tautų regioninės plėtros centras"@lt, "ÜRO Regionaalarengu Keskus"@et, "United Nations Centre for Regional Development"@en, "Centrum van de Verenigde Naties voor regionale ontwikkeling"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "United Nations Centre for Regional Development (UNCRD), established based on an agreement between the Government of Japan and the United Nations, strives to promote sustainable regional development in developing countries with a focus on development planning and management in the context of globalization and decentralization trends, and the growing concern towards global environmental issues and their impacts. UNCRD is administered by the Division for Sustainable Development of the United Nations Department of Economic and Social Affairs."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "UNCRD"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "UNCRD"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001240"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "VN-Instituut voor Ontwapeningsonderzoek"@nl, "UN Centre for Regional Development"@en, "Centrul ONU pentru Dezvoltare"@ro, "CNUDR"@fr, "CNUDR"@es, "FN:s center för regional utveckling"@sv, "CNUDR"@pt, "Centrum OSN pro regionální rozvoj"@cs, "Ċentru tan-NU għall-Iżvilupp Reġjonali"@mt, "Centrum OSN pre regionálny rozvoj"@sk, "ÜRO piirkondliku arengu keskus"@et, "Center ZN za regionalni razvoj"@sl, "UNCRD"@en, "Ośrodek ONZ ds. Rozwoju Regionalnego"@pl, "UNCRD"@el, "Център на ООН за регионално развитие"@bg, "Az ENSZ Leszerelési Kutatóintézete"@hu, "ANO Reģionālās attīstības centrs"@lv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNCRD_1971_0>;
