<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ed09416bf0d00e9b8e8f91ac27537377>.
<#ed09416bf0d00e9b8e8f91ac27537377> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/IMF>;
