    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Kummissjoni reġjonali tan-Nazzjonijiet Uniti"@mt, "Регионална комисија УН"@sr, "Regionalna komisija Ujedinjenih naroda"@hr, "Regional kommission inom FN"@sv, "Regionálna komisia OSN"@sk, "Regionální komise OSN"@cs, "Comisión Regional de las Naciones Unidas"@es, "Coimisiún réigiúnach na Náisiún Aontaithe"@ga, "Komisja regionalna ONZ"@pl, "Jungtinių Tautų Regioninė komisija"@lt, "Commission régionale des Nations unies"@fr, "Commissione regionale delle Nazioni Unite"@it, "Comisie regională a Națiunilor Unite"@ro, "Regionalkommission der Vereinten Nationen"@de, "Регионална комисия на ООН"@bg, "Az ENSZ regionális bizottsága"@hu, "De Forenede Nationers regionale kommission"@da, "ÜRO piirkondlik komisjon"@et, "YK:n alueellinen toimikunta"@fi, "Regionale commissie van de Verenigde Naties"@nl, "Περιφερειακή επιτροπή των Ηνωμένων Εθνών"@el, "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas reģionālā komisija"@lv, "United Nations regional commission"@en, "Regionalna komisija Združenih narodov"@sl, "Comissão Regional das Nações Unidas"@pt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Regional Commissions are the regional outposts of the United Nations and represent an integral part of the regional institutional landscape. Stationed in five regions of the world, they share the key objectives of aiming to foster economic integration at the sub-regional and regional levels, promoting the regional implementation of internationally agreed development goals, including the Millennium Development Goals (MDGs), and to support regional sustainable development by contributing to bridging economic, social and environmental gaps among their member countries and sub-regions."@en, "Organes subsidiaires. Les cinq commissions régionales sont la CEA, la CEE, la CEPALC, la CESAP et la CESAO."@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "UNREGICOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001189"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "UNREGICOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Commission régionale ONU"@fr, "Comisión regional ONU"@es, "JT regioninė komisija"@lt, "Περιφερειακή Επιτροπή του ΟΗΕ"@el, "UN regional commission"@en, "Comissão regional ONU"@pt, "Comisia regională ONU"@ro, "Regional FN-kommission"@da, "Regional kommission (FN)"@sv, "RC"@en, "Regionalna komisija ZN"@sl, "ANO reģionālā komisija"@lv, "Kummissjoni Reġjonali ONU"@mt, "Commissione regionale dell’ONU"@it, "Regionalkommission UNO"@de, "Regionale VN-commissie"@nl, "YK:n aluekomissio"@fi;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNREGICOM_1947_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "UNREGICOM";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "UNREGICOM";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "UNREGICOM";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1947-03-28";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "UNREGICOM";
