<#fcc988f6a3c75e608cefcbd6af45eeec> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/IBE>;
