<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5861c0207c3ef8df34f8b7a4ab9221d4>.
<#5861c0207c3ef8df34f8b7a4ab9221d4> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNCND>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:18.108Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#5861c0207c3ef8df34f8b7a4ab9221d4> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNCND> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas Narkotisko vielu komisija"@lv, "Commissione delle Nazioni Unite sugli stupefacenti"@it, "YK:n huumeidenvastainen toimikunta"@fi, "Ühinenud Rahvaste Organisatsiooni narkootikumide komisjon"@et, "Komise OSN pro narkotika"@cs, "Coimisiún na Náisiún Aontaithe um Dhrugaí Támhshuanacha"@ga, "Komisja ONZ ds. Środków Odurzających"@pl, "Jungtinių Tautų Narkotinių medžiagų komisija"@lt, "Commissie Verdovende Middelen van de Verenigde Naties"@nl, "FN:s narkotikakommission"@sv, "De Forenede Nationers Narkotikakommission"@da, "Komisija Ujedinjenih naroda za opojne droge"@hr, "Комисия на ООН по наркотичните вещества"@bg, "Commission des Nations unies des stupéfiants"@fr, "Kummissjoni tan-Nazzjonijiet Uniti dwar id-Drogi Narkotiċi"@mt, "Comisión de Estupefacientes de las Naciones Unidas"@es, "Az ENSZ Kábítószer-bizottsága"@hu, "Comisia Organizației Națiunilor Unite privind stupefiantele"@ro, "Επιτροπή των Ηνωμένων Εθνών για τα Ναρκωτικά"@el, "Komisija Združenih narodov za mamila"@sl, "United Nations Commission on Narcotic Drugs"@en, "Suchtstoffkommission der Vereinten Nationen"@de, "Komisia OSN pre omamné látky"@sk, "Comissão dos Estupefacientes das Nações Unidas"@pt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Commission on Narcotic Drugs (CND) was established by the Economic and Social Councilresolution 9(I), to assist the ECOSOC in supervising the application of the international drug control treaties. In 1991, the General Assembly (GA) further expanded the mandates of the CND to enable it to function as the governing body of the UNODC, and to approve the budget of the Fund of the United Nations International Drug Control Programme, which accounts for over 90 per cent of the resources available to the United Nations for drug control."@en, "La Commission des stupéfiants (CND) a été créée par le Conseil économique et social dans sa résolution 9(I), afin d’assister le Conseil dans le suivi de la mise en œuvre des conventions internationales sur le contrôle des drogues. En 1991, l’Assemblée générale a élargi le mandat de la CND afin de lui permettre d’assumer le rôle d’organe directeur de l’Office des Nations Unies contre la drogue et le crime et d’approuver le budget du Fonds du programme des Nations Unies pour le contrôle international des drogues, qui représente plus de 90 % des ressources à disposition des Nations Unies pour le contrôle des drogues."@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "UNCND"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "UNCND"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001210"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "De forenede Nationers økonomiske og sociale Råds kommission for narkotiske midler"@da, "Kommission für Suchtstoffe des Wirtschafts- und Sozialrats der Vereinten Nationen"@de, "Commissie voor verdovende middelen van de Economische en Sociale Raad van de Verenigde Naties"@nl, "Comision de estupefacientes del Consejo Economico y Social de las Naciones Unidas"@es, "Narkotikakommissionen"@da, "An Coimisiún um Dhrugaí Támhshuanacha"@ga, "Kummissjoni dwar id-Drogi Narkotiċi"@mt, "Narkotinių medžiagų komisija"@lt, "CND"@sl, "CND"@da, "CND"@lv, "CND"@mt, "CND"@cs, "Komisia pre omamné látky"@sk, "CND"@fi, "CND"@pt, "Commissione stupefacenti"@it, "CND"@en, "CND"@it, "Kábítószer-bizottság"@hu, "Commission des stupéfiants du Conseil économique et social des Nations Unies"@fr, "CND"@fr, "Комисия по наркотичните вещества"@bg, "CND"@ro, "Suchtstoffkommission"@de, "Narkootiliste ainete komisjon"@et, "Επιτροπή για τα Ναρκωτικά του Οικονομικού και Κοινωνικού Συμβουλίου των Ηνωμένων Εθνών"@el, "Comisión de Estupefacientes"@es, "Commission on Narcotic Drugs"@en, "Komisja ds. Środków Odurzających"@pl, "Comissão dos Estupefacientes"@pt, "Commission on Narcotic Drugs of the Economic and Social Council on the United Nations"@en, "Commission des stupéfiants"@fr, "Komise pro narkotika"@cs, "Comisia privind stupefiantele"@ro, "Narkotisko vielu komisija"@lv, "Commissione stupefacenti del Consiglio economico e sociale delle Nazioni Unite"@it, "Commissie Verdovende Middelen"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNCND_1946_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "UNCND";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "UNCND";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "UNCND";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1946-02-15";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "UNCND";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNO>
}
