    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "central mechanism within the Secretariat of the United Nations to supply the statistical needs and coordinating activities of the global statistical system; the United Nations Statistics Division serves under the United Nations Department of Economic and Social Affairs and is overseen by the United Nations Statistical Commission"@en;
