    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas Sociālo lietu komisija"@lv, "Comisión Social de las Naciones Unidas"@es, "Commission sociale des Nations unies"@fr, "United Nations Social Commission"@en, "YK:n sosiaalitoimikunta"@fi, "Comissão Social das Nações Unidas"@pt, "Ühinenud Rahvaste Organisatsiooni sotsiaalkomisjon"@et, "Kummissjoni Soċjali tan-Nazzjonijiet Uniti"@mt, "Социална комисия на Обединените нации"@bg;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Social Commission was established by ECOSOC res. 10 (II) (1946). Its purpose was to advise ECOSOC on social policies of a general character and, in particular, on all matters in the social field not covered by the specialised inter-governmental agencies."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "UNSOCCOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "UNSOCCOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001202"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
