    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "United Nations High-level Political Forum on Sustainable Development"@en, "Fóram Ardleibhéil Polaitíochta na Náisiún Aontaithe um Fhorbairt Inbhuanaithe"@ga, "Forum politico di alto livello sullo sviluppo sostenibile"@it, "Forum politique des Nations unies de haut niveau pour le développement durable"@fr, "Politični forum na visoki ravni za trajnostni razvoj"@sl, "Politické fórum na vysokej úrovni pre udržateľný rozvoj"@sk, "Forum Polityczne Wysokiego Szczebla ds. Zrównoważonego Rozwoju"@pl, "Fórum Político de Alto Nível para o Desenvolvimento Sustentável"@pt, "Forum Politiku ta’ Livell Għoli dwar l-Iżvilupp Sostenibbli"@mt, "Forumul politic la nivel înalt pentru dezvoltare durabilă"@ro, "Politiska högnivåforumet för hållbar utveckling"@sv, "YK:n kestävän kehityksen korkean tason poliittinen foorumi"@fi, "Säästva arengu kõrgetasemeline poliitiline foorum"@et, "Hochrangiges politisches Forum für nachhaltige Entwicklung"@de, "Politiek forum op hoog niveau voor duurzame ontwikkeling"@nl, "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas Augsta līmeņa politiskais forums ilgtspējīgas attīstības jautājumos"@lv, "Aukšto lygio politinis forumas darnaus vystymosi srityje"@lt, "Politisk Forum på Højt Niveau vedrørende Bæredygtig Udvikling"@da, "Политически форум на високо равнище за устойчивото развитие"@bg, "Foro Político de Alto Nivel de las Naciones Unidas sobre el Desarrollo Sostenible"@es, "A fenntartható fejlődéssel foglalkozó magas szintű politikai fórum"@hu, "Πολιτικό φόρουμ υψηλού επιπέδου για τη βιώσιμη ανάπτυξη"@el, "Politički forum Ujedinjenih naroda na visokoj razini o održivom razvoju"@hr, "Politické fórum OSN na vysoké úrovni na téma udržitelného rozvoje"@cs;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The high-level political forum, consistent with its universal intergovernmental character, shall provide political leadership, guidance and recommendations for sustainable development, follow up and review progress in the implementation of sustainable development commitments, enhance the integration of the three dimensions of sustainable development in a holistic and cross-sectoral manner at all levels and have a focused, dynamic and action-oriented agenda, ensuring the appropriate consideration of new and emerging sustainable development challenges."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COB0001216"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "UNHLPF"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "UNHLPF"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "An Fóram Ardleibhéil Polaitíochta"@ga, "Политически форум на високо равнище"@bg, "Augsta līmeņa politiskais forums"@lv, "Politiek forum op hoog niveau"@nl, "High-level Political Forum"@en, "Aukšto lygio politinis forumas"@lt, "Forum politique de haut niveau"@fr, "Kestävän kehityksen foorumi"@fi, "Forumul politic la nivel înalt"@ro;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNHLPF_2013_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "UNHLPF";
