    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "United Nations Economic Commission for Asia and the Far East"@en, "Apvienoto Nāciju Organizācijas Ekonomikas komisija Āzijai un Tālajiem Austrumiem"@lv, "Comisión Económica para Asia y el Lejano Oriente de las Naciones Unidas"@es, "Commission économique des Nations unies pour l’Asie et l’Extrême-Orient"@fr, "YK:n Aasian ja Kaukoidän talouskomissio"@fi, "Jungtinių Tautų Azijos ir Tolimųjų Rytų ekonomikos komisija"@lt, "Kummissjoni Ekonomika tan-Nazzjonijiet Uniti għall-Ażja u l-Lvant Imbiegħed"@mt, "Comissão Económica das Nações Unidas para a Ásia e o Extremo Oriente"@pt, "Ühinenud Rahvaste Organisatsiooni Aasia ja Kaug-Ida majanduskomisjon"@et, "Икономическа комисия на ООН за Азия и Далечния изток"@bg;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Established in Shanghai, China, as the Economic Commission for Asia and the Far East to assist in post-war economic reconstruction, (...). The name was changed in 1974 to reflect both the economic and social aspects of development and the geographic location of its member countries."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "UNECAFE"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001197"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "UNECAFE"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "CEPALO"@es, "Commission économique pour l’Asie et l’Extrême-Orient"@fr, "ECAFE"@de, "ECAFE"@fi, "ECAFE"@nl, "Wirtschaftskommission für Asien und den Fernen Osten"@de, "Aasian ja Kaukoidän taloudellinen toimikunta"@fi, "ECAFE"@da, "ECAFE"@it, "ECAFE"@en, "Commissione economica per l’Asia e l’Estremo Oriente"@it, "Economic Commission for Asia and the Far East"@en, "Economische Commissie voor Azie en het Verre Oosten"@nl, "Comissão Económica para a Ásia e o Extremo Oriente"@pt, "Den Økonomiske Kommission for Asien og Det Fjerne Østen"@da, "Οικονομική Επιτροπή για την Ασία και την Απω Ανατολή"@el, "CEAEO"@pt, "Comisión Económica para Asia y el Lejano Oriente"@es, "CEAEO"@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNECAFE_1947_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "UNECAFE";
