<#49a78f0e1ccce724a21126b42b7fb109> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/OHCHR> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Valné zhromaždenie Organizácie Spojených národov"@sk, "Zgromadzenie Ogólne Narodów Zjednoczonych"@pl, "Adunarea Generală a Organizației Națiunilor Unite"@ro, "Uffiċċju tal-Kummissarju Għoli għad-Drittijiet tal-Bniedem"@mt, "Служба на върховния комисар по човешките права"@bg, "Ύπατη Αρμοστεία των Ηνωμένων Εθνών για τα Δικαιώματα του Ανθρώπου"@el, "Канцеларија Високог комесара за људска права"@sr, "Alto Comissariado para os Direitos do Homem"@pt, "Ured visokog povjerenika za ljudska prava"@hr, "ÜRO inimõiguste ülemvoliniku büroo"@et, "Augstā cilvēktiesību komisāra birojs"@lv, "Vyriausiojo žmogaus teisių komisaro biuras"@lt, "Haut-Commissariat aux droits de l’homme"@fr, "Bureau van de Hoge Commissaris voor de rechten van de mens"@nl, "Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights"@en, "Amt des Hohen Kommissars für Menschenrechte"@de, "FN’s højkommissær for menneskerettigheders kontor"@da, "Úřad vysokého komisaře OSN pro lidská práva"@cs, "Az ENSZ Emberi Jogi Főbiztosának Hivatala"@hu, "Oficina del Alto Comisionado para los Derechos Humanos"@es, "Ufficio dell’Alto commissario per i diritti umani"@it, "Birleşmiş Milletler İnsan Hakları Yüksek Komiserliği"@tr, "Oifig an Ard-Choimisinéara um Chearta an Duine"@ga, "YK:n ihmisoikeusvaltuutetun toimisto"@fi, "Kontoret för FN:s högkommissarie för mänskliga rättigheter"@sv, "Urad visokega komisarja za človekove pravice"@sl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Le Haut-Commissariat des Nations Unies aux droits de l’homme représente l’engagement du monde envers les idéaux universels de la dignité humaine. Ces priorités comprennent un plus gran engagement des pays, une collaboration étroite avec nos partenaires aux niveaux national et local, afin de garantir l’application des normes internationales des droits de l’homme sur le terrain; un rôle de leader plus prononcé pour la Haut-Commissaire; un partenariat renforcé avec la société civile et les organisations des Nations Unies.\""@fr, "The Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights (OHCHR) represents the world’s commitment to universal ideals of human dignity. OHCHR’s thematic priorities are strengthening international human rights mechanisms; enhancing equality and countering discrimination; combating impunity and strengthening accountability and the rule of law; integrating human rights in development and in the economic sphere; widening the democratic space; and early warning and protection of human rights in situations of conflict, violence and insecurity."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "OHCHR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001228"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "OHCHR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Oficina del Alto Comisionado de las Naciones Unidas para los Derechos Humanos"@es, "Oficiul Înaltului Comisar al Națiunilor Unite pentru Drepturile Omului"@ro, "JT vyriausiojo žmogaus teisių komisaro biuras"@lt, "Biuro Wysokiego Komisarza NZ ds. Praw Człowieka"@pl, "OHCHR"@en, "OHCHR"@da, "OHCHR"@de, "Urad visokega komisarja Združenih narodov za človekove pravice"@sl, "ACNUDH"@es, "Amt des Hohen Kommissars der Vereinten Nationen für Menschenrechte"@de, "Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights"@en, "ACDH"@pt, "ΥΑ"@el, "HCDH"@fr, "Υπατη Αρμοστεία των Ηνωμένων Εθνών για τα ανθρώπινα δικαιώματα"@el, "Alto Comissariado das Nações Unidas para os Direitos do Homem"@pt, "Haut-Commissariat des Nations Unies aux droits de l’homme"@fr, "De Forenede Nationers Højkommissariat for Menneskerettigheder"@da, "OHCRH"@nl, "OHCRH"@sk, "OHCRH"@it, "OHCRH"@hr, "Biuro Wysokiego Komisarza Narodów Zjednoczonych ds. Praw Człowieka"@pl, "OHCRH"@sl, "OHCRH"@lv, "OHCRH"@pl, "OHCRH"@lt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/OHCHR_1997_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "OHCHR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "OHCHR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "OHCHR";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1997-09-15";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "OHCHR";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/UNO>
}
