    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Fem permanenta medlemmar"@sv, "Fünf ständige Mitglieder"@de, "Pet stalnih članica (P5)"@hr, "De fem permanente medlemmer"@da, "Cinque membri permanenti"@it, "Vijf permanente leden"@nl, "Pět stálých členů"@cs, "Penkios nuolatinės narės"@lt, "Πέντε μόνιμα μέλη"@el, "Pięciu stałych członków"@pl, "Cúig Chomhalta Bhuana"@ga, "Петима постоянни членове"@bg, "Pieci pastāvīgie locekļi"@lv, "Cinco miembros permanentes"@es, "Päť stálych členov"@sk, "Öt állandó tag"@hu, "Ħames Membri Permanenti"@mt, "Cinq membres permanents"@fr, "Pet stalnih članic"@sl, "Viisi pysyvää jäsentä"@fi, "Cinco membros permanentes"@pt, "Viis alalist liiget"@et, "Five Permanent Members"@en, "Cinci membri permanenți"@ro;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The permanent members of the United Nations Security Council, also known as the Permanent Five, Big Five, or P5, include the following five governments: China, France, Russia, the United Kingdom, and the United States. The members represent the five great powers considered the victors of World War II. Each of the permanent members has the power to veto."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COB0001080"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "P5"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "P5"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Az ENSZ Biztonsági Tanácsának öt állandó tagja"@hu, "Die fünf ständigen Mitglieder des Sicherheitsrates der Vereinigten Nationen"@de, "Cinco permanentes"@pt, "Cinq permanents"@fr, "Cinco permanentes"@es, "Permanent Five"@en, "YK:n turvallisuusneuvoston viisi pysyvää jäsentä"@fi, "De fem permanente medlemmer af FN’s Sikkerhedsråd"@da, "Pięciu stałych członków Rady Bezpieczeństwa ONZ"@pl, "The five permanent members of the UN Security Council"@en, "P5"@en, "P5"@fr, "P5"@de, "Les cinq membres permanents du Conseil de sécurité des Nations unies"@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/P5_1945_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "P5";
